  Description:	Return the plaintext caption of a taxon from a taxon list item 
  Parameters:	@Key  
			@Caption OUTPUT

  Created:	March 2004

  Last revision information:
    $Revision: 2 $
    $Date: 2/02/09 14:35 $
    $Author: Pauldavies $

\*===========================================================================*/
